%%{init: {'theme': 'redux'}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant User as 用户
    participant Feishu as 飞书群聊
    participant Gateway as OpenClaw Gateway
    participant GH as GitHub CLI
    participant GHAction as GitHub Action
    participant Webhook as 飞书机器人Webhook

    User->>Feishu: 输入股票分析消息
    Feishu->>Gateway: 推送消息事件

    Note over Gateway: 识别需要分析的股票

    Gateway->>GH: gh run trigger

    GH->>GHAction: 触发Workflow

    Note over GHAction: 执行股票分析任务

    GHAction->>Webhook: POST 推送结果

    Webhook->>Feishu: 发送群聊消息

    Feishu-->>User: 展示分析结果
